@page "/interests"

<PageTitle>Interests | CAPECENIO</PageTitle>

<h2 class="mb-4">Beyond the Keyboard</h2>

<div class="content-card">
    <h4 class="accent-text">Aspirations in Uniformed Service</h4>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7;">
      Since I was young, I’ve been hooked on shooting games and tactical movies. I’ve always found the whole concept of weapons, strategy, and coordination really interesting, which is what got me into milsim and tactical stuff.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="content-card">
    <h4 class="accent-text">Gaming</h4>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7;">
        I enjoy competitive gaming because of the thrill and intensity it brings, especially the fast decision-making and constant need to improve. but I also like playing solo adventure games where I can explore, discover new things, and just get immersed in the experience.
    </p>
</div>

<div class="content-card">
    <h4 class="accent-text">Jack of all Trades</h4>
    <p style="color: var(--text-muted); line-height: 1.7;">
        I like trying a bit of everything. From running and calisthenics to playing guitar, coding, cooking, and gaming, I enjoy learning new things and picking up different skills. I wouldn’t say I’ve mastered everything, but I like being able to do a little of a lot and constantly finding new things to get into.
    </p>
</div>